## Limitations

The findings are based on available data and publications up to October 2023. Some sources may not have the most recent data or may not cover all aspects of the topic comprehensively. Additionally, the complexity of climate systems means that predictions and models can vary, and ongoing research may provide new insights into the relationship between climate change and hurricanes.